.TH AXXON-AUTOMATION 1 "November 2025" "Axxon Automation"
.SH NAME
axxon-automation \- provision Chrome, Slack, and Opera on Mint/Ubuntu systems
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B axxon-automation

.SH DESCRIPTION
.B axxon-automation
is a non-interactive setup utility that downloads and installs
Google Chrome, Slack, and Opera with logging and colored progress output.
It is intended for IT-managed Linux Mint and Ubuntu environments.

The tool must be run with root privileges. Logs are written to
.BR /usr/lib/axxon-automation/logs/ .

.SH OPTIONS
The command currently accepts no arguments.

.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
0
Success.
.TP
non-zero
An error occurred during download or installation.

